{"tid":594661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[未來撚阿廢請入] 焦土派大起底","createTime":"2018-03-16T04:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T09:33:52.000Z","uid":53687,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"633b120349b8ea3117562b74e1a15b71541b721c","tid":594661,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/inB74N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FinB74N.jpg&h=4ad39c53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬嶽等學者論文　指新移民較不傾向投泛民　易成威權收編目標<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/594214\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/594214</a><br />\n<br />\n根據屈焦派邏輯，邊個投保皇或廢票就係鬼，<br />\n咁呢班友支持一班投保皇佔多數嘅人嚟香港，咁即係鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：堅決反對投保皇，但泛民唔好再委過他人，唔去維護本地居民權利，仲好意思叫本土派投？"},{"pid":"9b62f6d46bc06c293fbf231115182933c0ea3b60","tid":594661,"uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:34:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手: 李怡都係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李怡︰泛民多年來對年輕人的抗爭行動，不是採取包容理解的態度，而是忙不迭地割席<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/592083/3?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/592083/3?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"3e9e73ac2b6d00c17c39ef07744cd827ae4d1278","tid":594661,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:45:31.000Z","msg":"[url]今次選舉慘敗其中一個原因：啟德蝗蟲邨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/589529/5?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/589529/5?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android[/url]<br />\n睇下人地點定義新移民先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ed3f5496e05623e192cadc33fc137cf6ed0f8","tid":594661,"uid":44525,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:45:46